                    <h5 style="margin-top: 10px; text-align:center; color: black">Next-Level Beats</h5>
                    <p style="text-align:center; color: black">Unlock the rhythm of your soul with MusicApp - where melody meets technology to create an immersive musical journey.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <div style="padding: 10px">
