                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <div style="padding: 10px">
                    <img style="margin-bottom: 10px" class="img-thumbnail" src="~/images/record-player-yellow.jpg" alt="..." />
                    <h5 style="margin-top: 10px; text-align:center; color: black">Sonic Oasis</h5>
                    <p style="text-align:center; color: black">Fuel your passion for music with our groundbreaking MusicApp. From catchy hooks to mind-blowing solos, we've got it all. Join the revolution and experience music like never before.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <div style="padding: 10px">
                    <img style="margin-bottom: 10px" class="img-thumbnail" src="~/images/ukulele.jpg" alt="..." />
                    <h5 style="margin-top: 10px; text-align:center; color: black">Passion Igniter</h5>
                    <p style="text-align:center; color: black">Discover the future of music exploration with MusicApp. Uncover hidden gems, rediscover old favorites, and embark on a sonic journey like no other.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
<section class="clean-block clean-hero">
    <div class="text">
            <p class="text-secondary-emphasis" style="background-color: rgba(249, 249, 249, 0.7); text-align:center; padding: 10px">
                Music possesses a remarkable power that transcends language and unites hearts and souls across the globe. It has the ability to inspire, uplift, and evoke a multitude of emotions within us. Through its enchanting melodies and poetic lyrics, music has the unique ability to ignite passion, spark revolutions, and foster connections between individuals from all walks of life. It is a universal language that breaks down barriers, evokes empathy, and unites us in moments of pure bliss. Whether in times of joy, sorrow, celebration, or contemplation, music stands as a constant companion, guiding us through the complexities of life and reminding us of the profound beauty that resides within us all.</p>
    </div>
</section>
<div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="card text-center clean-card">
            <img class="card-img-top w-100 d-block" src="/images/top-charts.jpg" style="height: 300px; border: 10px solid white">
            <div class="card-body info">
                <h4 class="card-title"><strong>Greatest All Time Hits</strong><br></h4>
                    <form method="post" asp-action="GetAllTimeSongs">
                        <div class="input-group-append">
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-info" type="submit">See Greatest Top Hits</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                <p class="card-text" style="margin-top: 10px">
                        Whether you're a fan of rock, pop, soul, or any genre in between, these legendary hits will captivate your senses and remind you why they have stood the test of time.<br>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="card text-center clean-card">
                <img class="card-img-top w-100 d-block" src="/images/singer.jpg" style="height: 300px; border: 10px solid white">
            <div class="card-body info">
                <h4 class="card-title"><strong>Top 50 Artists</strong><br></h4>
                    <form method="post" asp-action="GetTopByMonthlyListeners">
                        <div class="input-group-append">
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-info" type="submit">See Top Artists</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <p class="card-text" style="margin-top: 10px">
                        Discover the vocal prowess and magnetic artistry of these exceptional artists who captivate millions with their enchanting voices and have earned their place among the most celebrated voices of our time.<br>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
